Package: braincellann
Type: Package
Title: Brain Cell Marker Annotation Package
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Veronika Pak
Maintainer: The package maintainer <veronika.pak@mail.mcgill.ca>
Description: The 'braincellann' package is designed for the annotation of brain cell type-specific gene markers. 
    It provides functions to annotate gene markers using various databases such as the Human Protein Atlas 
    and integrates data for analysis and visualization. The package aims to streamline the process of 
    brain cell annotation and assist in data analysis workflows in single-cell transcriptomics studies.
